data.title: Full time Optometrist Needed in WVC
data.text:
Full-time optometrist needed at busy Shopko Optical in West Valley City, Utah. Optical is located in a standalone office, not in a retail store. Position is employed with option to work 4 days a week. Full benefits and PTO available. Staff does pretesting and insurance billing.

Shopko Optical is under new ownership since 2019. Company management is very supportive of doctors of optometry. Independent Shopko Optical Lab offers high-quality Ziess lenses. Come be a part of this rapidly growing company!

Contact Dr. Swain if interested.

cdswain95@gmail.com

Work Phone: 8018605100
